00106     void run()
00107     {
00108         execute("./apt-copynumber-wave \
00109                     -v 3 \
00110                     --cn-reference-input ../../../regression-data/data/copynumber/copynumber-cyto/Cytogenetics_Array/wave/Cytogenetics_Array_input.REF_MODEL \
00111                     --cn-reference-output " + testDir + "/Cytogenetics_Array/wave/Cytogenetics_Array_output.REF_MODEL \
00112                     --analysis additional-waves-reference-method.additional-wave-count=3.trim=2.0.percentile=0.75.demean=false.cn-qc-cutoff=0.27.snp-qc-cutoff=1.1.waviness-seg-count-cutoff=10.force=true.keep-temp-data=false \
00113                     --cychp-files ../../../regression-data/data/copynumber/copynumber-cyto/Cytogenetics_Array/wave/cychp_files.txt");
00114 
00115         bool bPassed = true;
00116 
00117         std::set<std::string> setIgnore;
00118         AffxString strFileName1 = "../../../regression-data/data/copynumber/copynumber-cyto/Cytogenetics_Array/wave/Cytogenetics_Array_output.REF_MODEL";
00119         AffxString strFileName2 = "" + testDir + "/Cytogenetics_Array/wave/Cytogenetics_Array_output.REF_MODEL";
00120         if (!affx::File5_File::equivalent(strFileName1, strFileName2, "Cyto2", "Parameters", setIgnore, 0, 1)) {bPassed = false;}
00121         if (!affx::File5_File::equivalent(strFileName1, strFileName2, "Cyto2", "AntigenomicProbes", setIgnore, 0, 1)) {bPassed = false;}
00122         if (!affx::File5_File::equivalent(strFileName1, strFileName2, "Cyto2", "MedianSignals", setIgnore, 0, 1)) {bPassed = false;}
00123         if (!affx::File5_File::equivalent(strFileName1, strFileName2, "Cyto2", "ProbeEffects", setIgnore, 0, 1)) {bPassed = false;}
00124         if (!affx::File5_File::equivalent(strFileName1, strFileName2, "Cyto2", "SNPPosteriors", setIgnore, 0, 1)) {bPassed = false;}
00125         if (!affx::File5_File::equivalent(strFileName1, strFileName2, "Cyto2", "SketchCN", setIgnore, 0, 1)) {bPassed = false;}
00126         if (!affx::File5_File::equivalent(strFileName1, strFileName2, "Cyto2", "SketchSNP", setIgnore, 0, 1)) {bPassed = false;}
00127         if (!affx::File5_File::equivalent(strFileName1, strFileName2, "Cyto2", "WaveCorrection", setIgnore, 0, 1)) {bPassed = false;}
00128 
00129         if (bPassed) {numPassed++;} else {numFailed++;}
00130     }
